OL,3,CBarton House evacuation affected us
OL,4,C'mentally, financially and physically'
OL,6,FFive families evacuated into hotels
OL,7,Fafter their council flats were deemed
OL,8,Funsafe have told ITV News of the
OL,9,Fdevastating impact it's had on their
OL,10,Fchildren.
OL,12,FThey live in Bristol's oldest tower
OL,13,Fblock - Barton House - which due to
OL,14,Fstructural safety concerns.
OL,16,FBut the families, who do not want to
OL,17,Fbe identified, say they are reluctant
OL,18,Fto go back after seeing their
OL,19,Fchildren's health and wellbeing
OL,20,Fdeteriorate.
