OL,3,CBarton House evacuation affected us
OL,4,C'mentally, financially and physically'
OL,6,FOne mother said her son developed
OL,7,Fsevere anxiety following the emergency
OL,8,Fevacuation.
OL,10,FShe said: "The hardest thing has been
OL,11,Fseeing my child struggle with extreme
OL,12,Fanxiety which has stopped him from
OL,13,Feating and sleeping. It was a
OL,14,Fnightmare to see my child lay in a bed
OL,15,Funable to go to school for two
OL,16,Fcontinuous weeks - unable to eat and
OL,17,Fchest pains - all because of this
OL,18,Fanxiety."
