OL,4,C'mentally, financially and physically'
OL,6,FAnother mother said her daughter
OL,7,Fstarted self harming while staying in
OL,8,Fa hotel.
OL,10,FShe said: "When all this happened it
OL,11,Fjust affected my daughter mentally.
OL,12,FShe was a really strong girl. While we
OL,13,Fwere staying in a hotel I found out my
OL,14,Fdaughter self harmed - it was really
OL,15,Fhard for me. I just felt like I had no
OL,16,Fcontrol of the situation and her
OL,17,Fmental health has just got worse."
