OL,3,CBarton House evacuation affected us
OL,4,C'mentally, financially and physically'
OL,6,FIn November, the 14 storey block was
OL,7,Fevacuated when engineers feared their
OL,8,Fwere structural issues with the
OL,9,Fbuilding.
OL,11,FA more in depth surveys concluded the
OL,12,Fstructure was safe, but improved fire
OL,13,Fsafety measures have been installed.
OL,15,FBut the upheaval and trauma has
OL,16,Fimpacted many residents including the
OL,17,Ffive families who said: "It's
OL,18,Fdifficult enough as it is for a
OL,19,Fparent, let alone our children to go
OL,20,Fback to a building that has been
OL,21,Fdeemed unsafe.
