OL,6,F"It has affected us mentally,
OL,7,Ffinancially and physically."
OL,9,F"The children are scared, they're
OL,10,Fasking questions that I cannot answer."
OL,12,FIn a statement Bristol City Council
OL,13,Fsaid: "Throughout this difficult
OL,14,Fperiod we have continued to provide
OL,15,Ffree accommodation, meals, transport
OL,16,Fand access to support services for
OL,17,Fresidents.
